description: Universal Labs provides a decentralized personal cloud storage ecosystem powered by Ubbey Box and the Ownership Protocol (OWP), which enables ownership exchange of digital and physical assets in a peer-to-peer way. While securely storing one's files in a decentralized network, a user can also utilize Ubbey Box to mine Ubbey's native token by partaking in the network. Ease of use would allow users to freely use Ubbey Box like any other personal devices such as phones.
name: Universal Labs
